member.name: ID2D1SvgAttribute.Clone
member.summary: Creates a clone of this attribute value. On creation, the cloned attribute is not set on any element.
member.param: Specifies the attribute value to clone.
member.returns: This method returns an HRESULT success or error code.

member.name: ID2D1SvgAttribute.GetElement
member.summary: Returns the element on which this attribute is set. Returns null if the attribute is not set on any element.
member.param: When this method completes, this will contain a pointer to the element on which this attribute is set.
